{"tid":810531,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"逆襲美國專挑洋妞拍片賣　網友淚讚他18cm「為國爭光」","createTime":"2018-09-08T05:08:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-08T06:18:27.000Z","uid":48083,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d60dd8f18aa0f65183593229d174e5e74226179c","tid":810531,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T05:08:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/08/130809_73e72f099925a6d137188a9ed013ce15.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F08%2F130809_73e72f099925a6d137188a9ed013ce15.png&h=9c88efd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「中國人不是東亞病夫！」位在美國加州的成人影視工作室「香蕉狂熱」（Banana Fever），去年成立以來主打亞裔男優搭配西洋女星，小成本製作雖略顯粗糙，但仍在A片愛好者刮起一陣不小旋風，連一向不重視版權的中國網友，基於民族情感都群起呼籲同胞要支持正版，「多虧了他們，我們才能讓白人也知道中國人一點都不短！」 「表演要給一個大大的讚，貼近真實，女優不會莫名其妙的怪叫，不刻意，第一視角，也更有代入感！」美國成人影業歷史發展悠久，但長期以來亞裔男優的表演卻是少之又少，加州影視工作室「汝」相中了這一點成立了香蕉狂熱，專門販售華裔男星激戰西洋女星的動作片，不少中國網友看過後佳評如潮，直呼導演、製作人根本是為國爭光，「我光聽到國罵就高潮了！」（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n&gt;&gt;加入蘋果日報粉絲團94即時94狂！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20180907/1425390/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20180907%2F1425390%2F&d=f5gKr6U84mP3KOVxb21sgi7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=f570297b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20180907%2F1425390%2F&h=3c4fcd1b\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20180907/1425390/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd0d6e11e76213155cd9bfff6e49084b15bb7bb6","tid":810531,"uid":28547,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T06:18:27.000Z","msg":"之後發現係日本仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\